- nvim: popup window in upper right        issue: 67
    - motivation: A tips file and a Bmods open manually, which makes me annoyed.
    - goal: to change some buffers of the popup window in upper right automatically depending on the filetype of the current buffer
    - description
        - [] In a popup window, the below files are displayed as buffers.
            - buffers
                - tips.*
                - Bmods.*
        - [] When you change the current buffer, the popup windows are closed automatically.
        - [] Based on the filetype of the current buffer, a new popup window opens automatically.
        - [] (future) enable colorscheme of buffers in the popup window
    - Note
        - [] Some files will appended to buffers.
